HOW DID IT HAPPEN
IN THE BOOK ?

29:54.160 --> 29:56.685
MOUTH-TO-MOUTH
RESUSCITATION.

29:56.790 --> 29:58.087
WHICH MAKES SENSE.

29:58.190 --> 30:01.250
NOT SOME FUCKING
MAGIC TEAR.

30:04.530 --> 30:05.724
Curses.

30:05.830 --> 30:07.468
What ?
What is it ?

30:07.570 --> 30:09.197
Nurse Caterwaul.

30:09.300 --> 30:11.507
Children !

30:11.610 --> 30:13.635
( cackling )

30:13.740 --> 30:15.901
I CAN'T EVEN
WATCH THIS ANYMORE !

30:16.010 --> 30:18.444
BILLY, CHILL,
IT'S JUST A VIDEO.

30:18.550 --> 30:19.972
BUT THEY RUINED IT.

30:20.080 --> 30:23.049
THEY'RE LIKE
SO FUCKING SANITIZED,

30:23.150 --> 30:26.847
AND THERE'S NOT ANY REAL DANGER,
AND, I MEAN, COME ON.

30:26.950 --> 30:28.850
YOU CAN'T HAVE PEOPLE SAY
'PERSIMMONS AND PINEAPPLES'

30:28.960 --> 30:32.327
WITH AN AMERICAN ACCENT.

30:33.430 --> 30:35.591
WHAT A PIECE OF SHIT !

30:35.700 --> 30:38.521
HEY, IT'S NO BIG DEAL.

30:38.630 --> 30:41.599
YES, IT IS !

30:41.700 --> 30:43.292
IT WAS DAD,
YOU KNOW.

30:43.400 --> 30:44.867
DAD WHAT ?

30:44.970 --> 30:46.562
DAD WHO GAVE US
THE BOOK.

30:46.670 --> 30:47.659
REMEMBER ?

30:47.770 --> 30:48.907
KIND OF.

30:49.010 --> 30:51.706
