FOR CHRISTMAS.

30:51.810 --> 30:55.348
AND NOW DAD'S DEAD.

30:57.780 --> 31:01.216
AND OUR WHOLE
CHILDHOOD SUCKED

31:01.320 --> 31:05.689
AND NATHANIEL AND ISABEL
WAS THE ONLY GOOD THING

31:05.790 --> 31:07.724
WE HAD AND THEY
FUCKING RUINED IT.

31:07.830 --> 31:09.593
THEY DIDN'T RUIN IT.

31:09.700 --> 31:13.363
WE STILL HAVE IT.

31:13.470 --> 31:16.064
'LL ALWAYS
HAVE IT.

31:18.010 --> 31:21.730
WE ARE SO
DAMAGED, BREN.

31:21.840 --> 31:24.900
WE CAN GO ABOUT
OUR LIVES AND PRETEND

31:25.010 --> 31:26.875
THAT EVERYTHING'S
GONNA BE OKAY,

31:26.980 --> 31:30.472
BUT WE NEVER WILL BE,
NEVER !

31:30.580 --> 31:32.013
THAT'S NOT TRUE.

31:32.120 --> 31:34.884
WE'RE GETTING BETTER,
BOTH OF US.

31:34.990 --> 31:36.651
YOU ARE.

31:36.760 --> 31:39.752
I'M NOT.

31:39.860 --> 31:41.657
COME ON,
YOU KNOW YOU ARE.

31:41.760 --> 31:45.298
I REALLY DON'T
FEEL LIKE I AM.

31:48.640 --> 31:51.939
AND THOSE ARE
JUST FEELINGS.

31:53.570 --> 31:55.071
THIS IS JUST
RIGHT NOW.

31:55.180 --> 32:02.370
THE MOVIE AND DAD DYING
AND ME MOVING IN.

32:02.480 --> 32:04.482
IT'S BROUGHT UP
A LOT OF STUFF FOR YOU.

32:04.590 --> 32:06.785
YOU'LL WORK THROUGH IT,
IT'LL GET BETTER.

32:06.890 --> 32:09.358
PROMISE ?

32:09.460 --> 32:11.087
YEAH, I PROMISE.

32:11.190 --> 32:14.728
AND YOU'LL HELP ME ?

32:14.830 --> 32:17.424
OF COURSE
I'LL HELP YOU.

32:17.530 --> 32:20.328
STUPID.

32:24.670 --> 32:27.230
I'M SO GLAD
YOU'RE HERE.

32:29.840 --> 32:32.809
I LOVE YOU
SO MUCH, BREN.

32:32.910 --> 32:36.516
I LOVE YOU, TOO.

32:41.690 --> 32:42.588
BILLY !

32:42.690 --> 32:44.180
WHAT, WHAT ?

32:44.290 --> 32:45.985
DON'T EVER
DO THAT TO ME !

32:46.090 --> 32:48.126
IT WAS JUST A KISS.

32:48.230 --> 32:50.448
NO.

32:50.560 --> 32:51.959
NO, IT WASN'T.

32:52.070 --> 32:53.492
I WAS JUST
BEING AFFECT IONATE.

32:53.600 --> 32:54.794
I LOVE YOU.

32:54.900 --> 32:56.492
I GOTTA GO.

32:56.600 --> 32:57.498
WHAT ?

32:57.600 --> 32:58.862
BRENDA, WAIT.

32:58.970 --> 32:59.868
WHAT ?

32:59.970 --> 33:01.005
NO, OKAY.

33:01.110 --> 33:02.270
LET'S WATCH
ANOTHER VIDEO.

33:02.380 --> 33:04.405
C'MON, WE'LL WATCH
A GOOD ONE THIS TIME.

33:04.510 --> 33:05.738
BRENDA !

33:05.850 --> 33:07.670
( door slamming )
BRENDA !

33:13.020 --> 33:14.112
YEAH !

33:14.220 --> 33:17.155
( Latin music )

33:36.040 --> 33:37.598
SORRY.

33:38.610 --> 33:39.474
YOU OKAY,
YOU TIRED ?

33:39.580 --> 33:41.172
MAYBE.

33:41.280 --> 33:43.441
YOU WANT TO REST ?

33:43.550 --> 33:44.847
NO.

33:44.950 --> 33:46.542
YES.

33:46.650 --> 33:48.686
NO.

33:50.990 --> 33:53.129
ARE YOU OKAY ?

33:54.730 --> 33:57.028
MY HEART'S BEATING
SO FAST.

33:57.130 --> 34:00.122
I'M SO DIZZY.

34:00.230 --> 34:02.960
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

34:03.070 --> 34:05.436
BABY, WHAT'S WRONG ?

34:05.540 --> 34:07.132
I NEED SOME AIR.

34:07.240 --> 34:08.673
I'M GOING TO TAKE YOU
TO THE HOSPITAL.

34:08.780 --> 34:09.633
NO, MY PURSE.

34:09.740 --> 34:11.298
MY PILL THING.

34:12.780 --> 34:14.577
JESUS, VAN ESSA.

34:14.680 --> 34:15.874
THE XANAX.

34:15.980 --> 34:17.641
WHICH ONE'S
THE XANAX ?

34:17.750 --> 34:18.580
THE BLUE ONE.

34:18.690 --> 34:19.714
THE BLUE.

34:19.820 --> 34:21.117
WHICH BLUE ONE ?

34:27.830 --> 34:30.628
JUST HOLD
MY HAND, OKAY ?

34:30.730 --> 34:31.492
OKAY.

34:31.600 --> 34:32.726
JUST HOLD ON TO ME.

34:32.830 --> 34:34.764
OKAY, OKAY.

34:36.940 --> 34:38.965
MY MOTHER SAYS
YOU WON'T LEAVE.

34:39.070 --> 34:40.731
I HAD TO SEE YOU.

34:40.840 --> 34:42.205
CLAIRE, PLEASE,

34:42.310 --> 34:44.244
IT'S DRIVING ME CRAZY
THINKING YOU'RE MAD AT ME.

34:44.350 --> 34:45.476
I'M SUPPOSED TO MAKE
YOU FEEL BETTER ?

34:45.580 --> 34:47.104
CLAIRE, I DON'T
WANT THIS TO END.

34:47.210 --> 34:49.576
I NEED THIS.

34:50.680 --> 34:52.113
I NEED YOU.

34:52.220 --> 34:54.484
I'M SORRY.

34:54.590 --> 34:58.526
I JUST CAN'T BE WITH SOMEBODY
WHO'S THIS CONFUSED.

34:58.630 --> 35:01.155
I KNOW I'M CONFUSED.

35:01.260 --> 35:03.125
BUT THE ONE THING THAT
I AM COMPLETELY SURE OF

35:03.230 --> 35:04.697
IS THAT I LOVE YOU.

35:04.800 --> 35:07.064
AND I BELIEVE YOU.

35:07.170 --> 35:10.731
BUT I HAVE BEEN
THROUGH THIS BEFORE.

35:10.840 --> 35:14.537
I'M NOT SOME NURSE WHO'S HERE
TO TAKE CARE OF THE MISFITS.

35:14.640 --> 35:16.505
LOOK, I'M SORRY.

35:16.610 --> 35:18.168
BUT WHATEVER IT IS
YOU'RE GOING THROUGH

35:18.280 --> 35:19.406
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE
TO FIGURE IT OUT ON YOUR OWN.

35:19.510 --> 35:21.068
WE SHOULD
BE TOGETHER.

35:21.180 --> 35:24.513
WE'RE BOTH CRAZY,
WE'RE BOTH FUCKED-UP ARTISTS.

35:24.620 --> 35:27.145
I MEAN, WE HAVE
TO BE TOGETHER.

35:27.250 --> 35:30.515
I DON'T THINK SO.

35:31.560 --> 35:33.118
I'M GONNA
CHANGE YOUR MIND.

35:33.230 --> 35:34.356
I SWEAR.

35:34.460 --> 35:35.893
PLEASE, JUST
LEAVE ME ALONE.

35:36.000 --> 35:38.218
CLAIRE, I WOULD CUT OUT MY HEART
AND GIVE IT TO YOU IN A BOX

35:38.330 --> 35:39.592
IF IT WOULD
CHANGE ANYTHING.

35:39.700 --> 35:41.099
WELL, IT WOULD BECAUSE
YOU'D BE DEAD, OKAY ?

35:41.200 --> 35:42.895
GOODBYE !

35:50.680 --> 35:53.740
(crying )

35:53.850 --> 35:55.169
CLAIRE ?

36:05.960 --> 36:08.451
( Lucille )
DID YOU GET
TAYLOR OFF TO BED ?

36:08.560 --> 36:10.824
YEAH, I CAN'T BELIEVE
HOW MUCH SHE'S GROWN UP.

36:10.930 --> 36:14.093
SHE POLITELY
INFORMED US

36:14.200 --> 36:15.690
THAT SHE'S TOO OLD
TO PLAY WITH BARBIES NOW.

36:15.800 --> 36:18.098
AND INSISTED THAT SHE
READ US A BEDTIME STORY.

36:18.210 --> 36:20.303
SHE'S SMART,
DOING WELL IN SCHOOL.

36:20.410 --> 36:21.968
( Keith )
GOOD.

36:22.080 --> 36:25.106
SHE MISSES HER MOMMA, BUT WE
DEAL WITH THAT THE BEST WE CAN.

36:25.210 --> 36:26.905
SHE SEEMS HAPPY.

36:27.010 --> 36:28.272
I'M JUST GLAD
THIS IS WORKING OUT.

36:28.380 --> 36:30.678
OF COURSE
IT'S WORKING OUT.

36:30.780 --> 36:32.782
LUCILLE, CAN I HELP YOU
IN THE KITCHEN ?

36:32.890 --> 36:35.654
SURE, DAVID,
THAN KS.

36:40.830 --> 36:45.199
DAD, I NEED TO TALK
TO YOU ABOUT SOMETHING.

36:49.070 --> 36:51.436
LOOK, I UM...

36:51.540 --> 36:55.499
I KNOW THINGS
HAVEN'T ALWAYS BEEN

36:55.610 --> 36:57.407
SO SMOOTH BETWEEN
YOU AND ME.

36:57.510 --> 36:59.603
AND I'VE BEEN WORKING ON SOME
THINGS ABOUT MYSELF IN THERAPY.

36:59.710 --> 37:03.840
AND I'VE COME TO REALIZE THAT
I WAS PRETTY MUCH TRAUMATIZED

37:03.950 --> 37:06.214
BY THE WAY YOU PUNISHED ME
AND KARLA WHEN WE WERE KIDS.

37:06.320 --> 37:08.754
THAT WAS ABUSIVE.

37:08.860 --> 37:11.727
THAT WAS ABUSE.

37:11.830 --> 37:12.956
ABUSE.

37:13.060 --> 37:14.596
I KNOW YOU DID
THE BEST YOU COULD,

37:14.700 --> 37:16.190
AND YOU WERE PROBABLY JUST
REPEATING WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU,

37:16.300 --> 37:17.449
BUT IT DID
A NUMBER ON ME,

37:17.560 --> 37:19.027
AND I KNOW IT DID ONE
ON KARLA--

37:19.130 --> 37:20.563
OH, SO NOW I'M TO BLAME FOR YOUR
SISTER'S PROBLEMS WITH DRUGS ?

37:20.670 --> 37:22.160
NO, I'M NOT
BLAMING ANYONE.

37:22.270 --> 37:23.794
I JUST WANT
TO ACKNOWLEDGE THE TRUTH

37:23.900 --> 37:25.367
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED
SO I CAN FORGIVE YOU.

37:25.470 --> 37:28.439
YOU WANT
TO FORGIVE ME ?

37:28.540 --> 37:32.306
YEAH, SO WE CAN HAVE
A REAL RELATIONSHIP

37:32.410 --> 37:33.604
WHILE WE STILL HAVE TIME.

37:33.710 --> 37:36.372
WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT ?

37:36.480 --> 37:38.710
I DISCIPLINED MY CHILDREN
WHEN THEY DESERVED IT.

37:38.820 --> 37:41.550
I GAVE YOU A HOME,
I GAVE YOU FOOD TO EAT,

37:41.660 --> 37:43.287
I TAUGHT YOU
HOW TO BE A MAN.

37:43.390 --> 37:44.687
AND YOU WANT
TO FORGIVE ME ?

37:44.790 --> 37:46.826
YOU BETTER GET ON YOUR KNEES
AND THANK ME,

37:46.930 --> 37:49.194
AND MAYBE I'LL FORGIVE YOU
FOR BEING A GODDAMN FAGGOT.

37:49.300 --> 37:50.449
I'M SORRY.

37:50.560 --> 37:51.697
I THOUGHT YOU MIGHT--

37:51.800 --> 37:53.825
I SAID I WANT
TO HEAR YOU THANK ME !

37:58.200 --> 38:00.430
WHO YOU THINK
YOU PUSHING, BOY ?

38:00.540 --> 38:01.973
BOTH OF YOU,
STOP IT !

38:02.080 --> 38:04.173
MR. CHARLES, YOUR SON WAS ONLY
TRYING TO REACH OUT TO YOU.

38:04.280 --> 38:05.406
AND WHO THE FUCK
ARE YOU AGAIN ?

38:05.510 --> 38:07.569
I'M THE MAN YOUR SON
IS IN LOVE WITH.

38:07.680 --> 38:09.875
YEAH, WELL IT MAKES ME
SICK TO MY STOMACH.

38:09.980 --> 38:11.880
HOW THE FUCK CAN YOU
ACT SO GODDAMN SUPERIOR

38:11.990 --> 38:13.981
WHEN EVERYONE HERE KNOWS
THAT YOU BEAT YOUR KIDS,

38:14.090 --> 38:15.648
YOU CHEATED ON
YOUR WIFE--

38:15.760 --> 38:17.614
I DID NO SUCH THING,
HOW DARE YOU ?!

38:17.720 --> 38:19.756
KEITH, YOU NEED
TO TELL HIM !

38:19.860 --> 38:21.725
DAVID, THIS ISN'T
THE PLACE FOR YOU TO SAY
ANYTHING ABOUT THIS STUFF.

38:21.830 --> 38:23.957
IT'S NOT MY PLACE ?

38:24.060 --> 38:26.722
NO, THIS IS MY FAMILY,
STAY THE FUCK OUT OF IT !

38:29.340 --> 38:31.262
THEN I CAN'T BE HERE.

38:31.370 --> 38:34.533
DAVID--

38:36.340 --> 38:39.673
YOU SHOULD'VE KNOCKED HIS TEETH
OUT FOR WHAT HE SAID TO ME.

38:39.780 --> 38:43.375
YOU'RE PATHETIC.

38:44.350 --> 38:47.547
( X's "Los Angeles" playing )

38:49.320 --> 38:51.379
I KNOW, THIS IS
A LITTLE BIT DIFFERENT

38:51.490 --> 38:52.718
THAN THE MUSIC
MOMMY PLAYS, ISN'T IT ?

38:52.830 --> 38:54.752
BUT I JUST DON'T THINK
I CAN STAND TO HEAR

38:54.860 --> 38:56.191
THE WIGGLES SING
"DANCE THE OOBY DOOBY"

38:56.300 --> 38:57.699
ONE MORE TIME WITHOUT
TEARING MY HEAD OFF.

38:57.800 --> 38:58.994
( buzzer )

38:59.100 --> 39:00.624
IT'S OPEN,
COME ON UP !

39:00.730 --> 39:04.439
HEY, IT'S
THE PIZZA MAN !

39:04.540 --> 39:07.964
ARE YOU READY FOR YOUR FIRST
TASTE OF PEPPERONI, HUH ?

39:10.140 --> 39:11.505
BRENDA, HEY.

39:11.610 --> 39:14.579
I'M SORRY, I DIDN'T
KNOW WHERE ELSE TO GO.

39:14.680 --> 39:16.978
I DIDN'T HAVE YOUR
NUMBER UP HERE.

39:17.080 --> 39:18.047
NO, IT'S FINE,
COME ON IN.

39:18.150 --> 39:19.185
ARE YOU SURE ?

39:19.290 --> 39:20.917
I'M NOT INTERRUPTING
ANYTHING ?

39:21.020 --> 39:23.614
NO, LISA'S GONE.

39:23.720 --> 39:27.679
I'M JUST INTRODUCING MAYA
TO SOME MUSIC THAT DOESN'T SUCK.

39:30.030 --> 39:31.019
WHAT'S WRONG ?

39:31.130 --> 39:33.098
BILLY.

39:33.200 --> 39:37.637
LET ME PUT MAYA DOWN
IN HER PLAYPEN.

39:39.070 --> 39:41.573
EVER SINCE
YOUR FATHER DIED

39:41.680 --> 39:43.432
I'VE JUST FLITTED
FROM MAN TO MAN.

39:43.540 --> 39:45.144
I AM SO EMBARRASSED.

39:45.250 --> 39:47.138
WELL...

39:47.250 --> 39:50.139
I MEAN, LOOK.

39:50.250 --> 39:53.845
YOU GOT MARRIED
WHEN YOU WERE 19.

39:53.950 --> 39:55.383
THAT'S HOW OLD I AM.

39:55.490 --> 39:58.186
LOOK, YOU NEVER EVEN GOT
TO HAVE YOUR SEXUAL 20's,

39:58.290 --> 40:00.656
SO, WHY SHOULDN'T YOU
DO IT NOW ?

40:00.760 --> 40:02.694
I MEAN, YOU DON'T HAVE
TO WORRY ABOUT US ANYMORE.

40:02.800 --> 40:06.292
NO.

40:06.400 --> 40:10.029
DID YOU KNOW I GOT
PREGNANT THE FIRST TIME
I'D EVER HAD SEX ?

40:10.140 --> 40:12.802
OH MY GOD.

40:12.910 --> 40:15.276
WITH DAD ?

40:15.380 --> 40:17.007
OF COURSE.

40:17.110 --> 40:19.442
OKAY, I THOUGHT YOU WERE
JUST GONNA TO TELL ME

40:19.550 --> 40:21.916
I HAD SOME LIKE LOVE-CHILD
HALF BROTHER SOMEWHERE,

40:22.020 --> 40:24.341
WHICH I REALLY DON'T
THINK I COULD HANDLE NOW.

40:24.450 --> 40:26.042
NO, IT WAS NATE.

40:26.150 --> 40:28.755
NATHANIEL AND I HAD
TO GET MARRIED RIGHT AWAY.

40:28.860 --> 40:32.250
BOTH OUR FAMILIES
WERE MORTIFIED.

40:32.360 --> 40:37.753
IT CHANGED
MY LIFE FOREVER.

40:38.230 --> 40:40.460
WOW.

40:41.470 --> 40:43.893
DO YOU EVER WONDER
HOW YOUR LIFE

40:44.000 --> 40:46.264
WOULD BE DIFFERENT
IF THAT HADN'T HAPPENED ?

40:46.370 --> 40:47.962
I USED TO.

40:48.070 --> 40:50.004
NOT ANYMORE.

40:53.980 --> 40:55.811
WERE YOU AND DAD
IN LOVE WITH EACH OTHER ?

40:55.920 --> 40:57.069
OH, YES !

40:57.180 --> 40:59.444
VERY MUCH SO,
AT FIRST.

40:59.550 --> 41:01.984
DESPITE HOW
WE GREW APART,

41:02.090 --> 41:05.981
YOUR FATHER WAS
THE GREAT LOVE OF MY LIFE.

41:08.090 --> 41:10.229
AT LEAST YOU HAD THAT.

41:10.330 --> 41:12.161
I'M BEGINNING
TO THINK I NEVER WILL.

41:12.270 --> 41:14.534
YOU WILL,
EVERYONE DOES.

41:14.640 --> 41:18.633
BUT CHANCES ARE, IT WON'T BE
ANYTHING LIKE YOU EXPECT.

41:20.610 --> 41:21.907
I MISS DAD,
YOU KNOW ?

41:22.010 --> 41:26.071
I FEEL LIKE...

41:26.180 --> 41:29.172
I HATE HOW I JUST LIKE TOOK HIM
FOR GRANTED MY WHOLE LIFE,

41:29.280 --> 41:30.747
AND NOW HE'S GONE,

41:30.850 --> 41:32.784
AND IT'S TOO LATE FOR ME
TO EVER REALLY KNOW HIM,

41:32.890 --> 41:35.051
YOU KNOW,
LIKE AS AN ADULT.

41:35.160 --> 41:37.481
I MISS HIM TOO.

41:37.590 --> 41:40.957
THERE WILL NEVER BE
ANOTHER MAN

41:41.060 --> 41:42.857
WHO WILL LOVE ME WHEN
I'M YOUNG AND PRETTY,

41:42.960 --> 41:45.326
AND THEN ALWAYS HAVE
THAT PICTURE OF ME

41:45.430 --> 41:46.897
SOMEWHERE
IN HIS HEART.

41:47.000 --> 41:49.594
OH, MOM.

41:49.700 --> 41:51.338
YOU'RE SO PRETTY.

41:51.440 --> 41:54.204
GOD, YOU'RE BEAUTIFUL.

41:54.310 --> 41:57.529
WHY DO YOU THINK ALL THESE MEN
ARE ALWAYS HITTING ON YOU ?

41:57.640 --> 41:59.471
YOU'RE SO SWEET.

41:59.580 --> 42:03.016
BUT LOOK AT THE MEN !

42:03.120 --> 42:07.113
I'M SITTING HERE
CRYING OVER ARTHUR.

42:07.220 --> 42:08.517
ARTHUR !

42:08.620 --> 42:11.748
WHAT SHOULD
I DO ABOUT HIM ?

42:11.860 --> 42:14.624
RUN.

42:17.300 --> 42:19.461
I FEEL SORRY
FOR HIM THOUGH.

42:19.570 --> 42:21.492
HE'S SO NAIVE.

42:21.600 --> 42:24.660
I FEEL SORRY
FOR RUSSELL TOO.

42:24.770 --> 42:28.365
I MEAN,
I HATE HIM,

42:28.470 --> 42:34.045
BUT I FEEL
SORRY FOR HIM.

42:34.150 --> 42:37.074
MOM, WHY IS IT I ATTRACT EVERY
SCREWED-UP GUY IN THE STATE ?

42:37.180 --> 42:42.652
BECAUSE THEY CAN SEE
WHAT A KIND SOUL YOU HAVE,

42:42.760 --> 42:46.127
THAT YOU'RE CARING
AND SENSITIVE.

42:46.230 --> 42:50.018
IT'S THE TRUTH, CLAIRE,
YOU'RE AN ANGEL.

42:50.130 --> 42:54.328
BUT THE REAL QUESTION IS
WHY DO YOU LIKE THEM ?

42:54.430 --> 42:58.708
IT'S LIKE I'LL FALL FOR ANY GUY
WHO SHOWS ANY INTEREST IN ME.

42:58.810 --> 43:02.803
I GUESS WE ALL WANT
TO BE LOVED.

43:02.910 --> 43:05.743
IT'S HARD
TO SAY NO TO THAT,

43:05.850 --> 43:09.047
NO MATTER WHO
IT'S COMING FROM.

43:11.050 --> 43:12.984
I MEAN, RIGHT FROM
THE VERY BEGINNING

43:13.090 --> 43:14.853
THERE WAS THIS VOICE
INSIDE MY HEAD SAYING,

43:14.960 --> 43:16.359
"DON'T MOVE IN
WITH BILLY.

43:16.460 --> 43:18.109
DON'T MOVE IN
WITH BILLY."

43:18.220 --> 43:20.381
WHAT DO I DO ?

43:20.490 --> 43:22.151
I MOVE IN WITH BILLY.

43:22.260 --> 43:23.852
I'M SO SELF-DESTRUCT IVE.

43:23.960 --> 43:27.020
MAYBE YOU WANTED
TO BELIEVE THE WORLD

43:27.130 --> 43:29.132
IS A BETTER PLACE
THAN IT REALLY IS.

43:29.240 --> 43:31.492
SO, I'M AN IDIOT.

43:31.600 --> 43:36.173
NO, JUST A VERY
POSITIVE PERSON.

43:36.280 --> 43:38.032
THAT DOESN'T
SOUND LIKE ME.

43:38.140 --> 43:40.802
IT'S SCARY TO HOPE THINGS
ARE GONNA TURN OUT GOOD,

43:40.910 --> 43:42.377
BECAUSE THEN YOU'RE
TAKING THE RISK

43:42.480 --> 43:43.845
OF BEING DISAPPOINTED
IF THEY DON'T.

43:43.950 --> 43:48.444
WOW, YOU'VE REALLY
THOUGHT ABOUT THIS.

43:48.550 --> 43:51.656
